Package: predictsr
Title: Access the PREDICTS database from the Natural History Museum, London
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Connor", "Duffin", , "connor.duffin@nhm.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fetches the 2016 v1.1. PREDICTS database and relevant metadata from
  the Data Portal at the Natural History Museum, London - a dataset of 3,278,056
  measurements, from 26,194 sampling locations in 94 countries and
  representing 47,089 species. Data were collated from 480 existing spatial
  comparisons of local-scale biodiversity exposed to different intensities and
  types of anthropogenic pressures, from sites around the world. These data are
  licensed with a CC BY-NC 4.0 license.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
